<body>
<h1>ROCK.PAPER.SCISSORS</h1>
<h2>Do you dare take on THE COMPUTER??</h2>
<p>ROCK beats SCISSORS.....SCISSORS beats PAPER.....PAPER beats ROCK</p>
<h3>Enter your name to start the best RPS game you will ever play...</h3>
<div align="center"><i class="em em-fist"></i><i class="em em-newspaper"></i><i class="em em-scissors"></i></div>
<form action="/name" method="post">
  <label for="player_name">
    Player name <input type="text" name="player_name">
  </label>
  <input type="submit" value="May the battle commence!">
</form>
<img src="https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/660/media/images/74580000/jpg/_74580127_162317629(1).jpg" alt="Three hands demonstrating RPS" class="hands"/>
